\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Having decided 
\f2\i when
\f0\i0  to rebalance, the next challenge is 
\f2\i how
\f0\i0 \'97identifying the optimal set of trades that bring the portfolio back toward target exposures while balancing risk, cost, and other constraints. AI extends classical solvers by integrating predictive forecasts and advanced heuristics.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

